@startuml
title Sơ đồ Tuần tự - Thêm Chiến dịch Khuyến mãi
actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Browser" as UI
participant "CampaignAdminApiController" as Controller
participant "CampaignService" as Service
participant "CampaignRepository" as Repository
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> UI: Điền thông tin Khuyến mãi\n(Tên, Giảm giá, Ngày bắt đầu/kết thúc) & Submit
activate UI
UI -> Controller: POST /api/admin/campaigns (CampaignUpsertRequest)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: create(req)
activate Service

Service -> Service: Validate Request Data
Service -> Repository: save(Campaign)
activate Repository
Repository -> DB: INSERT INTO campaigns
activate DB
DB --> Repository: Success
deactivate DB
Repository --> Service: Return saved Campaign
deactivate Repository

Service --> Controller: Return CampaignResponse
deactivate Service
Controller --> UI: 200 OK (Campaign Details)
deactivate Controller
UI --> Admin: Hiển thị thông báo thành công
deactivate UI

@enduml
